  )"></span></span><span class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-[0.04em] lowercase">multica</span></a><p class="mt-4 max-w-[300px] text-[14px] leading-[1.7] text-white/50 sm:text-[15px]">Project management for human + agent teams. Open source, self-hostable, built for the future of work.</p><div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3"><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-white/40 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="https://x.com/MulticaAI"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="size-4" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"></path></svg></a><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-white/40 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="https://github.com/multica-ai/multica"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" class="size-4" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8a8 8 0 0 0 5.47 7.59c.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2 .37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82A7.65 7.65 0 0 1 8 4.84c.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.01 8.01 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8Z"></path></svg></a></div><div class="mt-6"><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-[11px] bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-[#0a0d12] transition-colors hover:bg-white/88" href="/login">Get started</a></div></div><div class="grid flex-1 grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-4"><div><h4 class="text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-white/40">Product</h4><ul class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2.5"><li><a class="text-[14px] text-white/50 transiti